short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy and paste hundreds of ASCII, Copypastas, and Symbols from a convenient browser popup!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: KEYCLIP_ is a simple to use extension that allows easy and immediate access to a wide variety of ASCII, copypastas, and symbols for all your serious or, not so serious needs. You can also add your own ASCII and quickly copy them to your computer's clipboard with the push of a button thanks to the built in save and copy function! This extension will be updated regularly with new features, things to copy and paste and you can contact us with suggestions, ASCII or copypastas for us to add in future updates, enjoy!
